{"id": 1611, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x草莓音乐节】哪首歌（or歌词）让你觉得孤独？", "description": "啊，人生中那些令人不知如何是好的脆弱时刻！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3044, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170405181258ylN0sML1bdeQkjYi.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-07T03:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 189440, "content": "陌生的城市啊，寂寞的角落里。也曾彼此安慰，也曾相拥哭泣。不管将会面对什么样的结局。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975336}, {"id": 189696, "content": "你我山前没相见 山后别相逢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665251}, {"id": 189441, "content": "你知道，烦恼会解决烦恼，新的刚来到，旧的就忘掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589135}, {"id": 190465, "content": "人生已经太匆匆，我好害怕总是泪眼朦胧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001150}, {"id": 189442, "content": "I hurt  myself today,To see if I still feel I focus on the pain ,the only thing that's real-《Hurt》", "image": "img/option/option/20170407172120gF75UNxR3zjDVqtf.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48994}, {"id": 189698, "content": "　　昨天我数到第二十五颗星星\n　　在北京第二十五个秋天的夜晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874616}, {"id": 189954, "content": "我一路向北，离开有你的季节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999227}, {"id": 189443, "content": "快乐当然有一点，不过寂寞更强烈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997368}, {"id": 189699, "content": "感谢那些人擦过刮过生活才有更美轮廓", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995547}, {"id": 189700, "content": "离开你我才发现自己那爱笑的眼睛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994749}, {"id": 208901, "content": "你怎么舍得让我的泪流向海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809902}, {"id": 189701, "content": "过了很久终于我愿抬头看\n你就在对岸等我勇敢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995844}, {"id": 194053, "content": "时间是一场有去无回的旅行，好的坏的都是风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008505}, {"id": 189446, "content": "人间  失 格", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821949}, {"id": 189702, "content": "为何爱判处终生孤寂，挣不脱，逃不过.    ——《默》", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889629}, {"id": 189958, "content": "大梦初醒，睁开眼睛\n睡眼惺忪，心空空\n大叫一声，无声\n大哭一场，如常", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999258}, {"id": 190471, "content": "没办法你要不要这样都得过下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001221}, {"id": 189448, "content": "Mad World", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130119}, {"id": 189705, "content": "我爱你❤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998061}, {"id": 189961, "content": "而我不再觉得失去是舍不得 有时候只愿意听你唱完一首歌", "image": "img/option/option/20170409135857fW53vIBTPczMR1ht", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999271}, {"id": 190729, "content": "你给我听好，想哭就要笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957080}, {"id": 189450, "content": "在遠離家鄉的出租屋裡看電影，看到特別搞笑的一幕，轉過身來想跟身邊的人會心大笑，回應的，只有自己的影子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891414}, {"id": 189451, "content": "外向的孤独患者有何不可。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924869}, {"id": 189707, "content": "If I lay here would you lie with me and just forget the world.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 369837}, {"id": 189452, "content": "长大以后，我只能奔跑...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997361}, {"id": 190220, "content": "不管你拥有什么，我们生来就是孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927278}, {"id": 189453, "content": "我不是一定要你回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997394}, {"id": 189709, "content": "苦命人\n相拥俯看 世上风霜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858055}, {"id": 190221, "content": "我想我会一直孤单，这样孤单一辈子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618373}, {"id": 189454, "content": "天灰灰，会不会，让我忘了你是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997398}, {"id": 189710, "content": "都是夜归人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949433}, {"id": 189455, "content": "《真的很在乎》---只剩一个人，宿醉的孤独，多无助，就仿佛，一场梦要落幕。\n最爱我的人，你们都身在何处，好想说，我真的很在乎。", "image": "img/option/option/20170407180755myAQD2tEns7zc0Se", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997393}, {"id": 189456, "content": "人群是那么像羊群", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993184}, {"id": 189712, "content": "I'm a creep. I'm a weirdo. I don't belong here.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 369837}, {"id": 189457, "content": "君是人间雪，我从白云客。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831557}, {"id": 189458, "content": "这里的故事你是否还记得", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997279}, {"id": 189714, "content": "这个保护我的人，这个爱惜我的人，这个相信我的人，这个把我握紧了又松开的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972592}, {"id": 189970, "content": "什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999138}, {"id": 189203, "content": "因为成长，我们逼不得已要分开", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996768}, {"id": 189459, "content": "我就是我，是颜色不一样的烟火?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871997}, {"id": 189715, "content": "You better let somebody love you, before it's too late.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585079}, {"id": 194323, "content": "末班车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009185}, {"id": 189204, "content": "《最冷一天》唯愿在剩余光线面前 留下两眼为见你一面", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523572}, {"id": 189460, "content": "在所有人事已非的景色里，我最喜欢你。", "image": "img/option/option/20170407182116MoKw0flRdVrhHPF5.jpg", "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114267}, {"id": 189716, "content": "东京テディベア -", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639677}, {"id": 219669, "content": "幻想过地久天长，憧憬过地老天荒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070808}, {"id": 189205, "content": "在这阳光灿烂的夜里", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948025}, {"id": 189461, "content": "人生就像烟圈，有时侬有时淡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997415}, {"id": 189973, "content": "观望着喜怒哀乐变换的故事\n我注定被寂寞囚牢", "image": "img/option/option/20170409153456oDPEHAvf0emKx2kM", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981964}, {"id": 190485, "content": "如此生活三十年直到大厦崩塌\n云层深处的黑暗啊淹没心底的景观", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717794}]}